jilles      2006/10/02 10:20:50 UTC	(20061002-6629)
  Log:
  Add get_source_name(), get_source_mask() and get_oper_name().
  These generate a name for a sourceinfo.
  The general idea is that get_source_name() and
  get_oper_name() are just a nick in the normal case
  where the user is logged in to an account with the
  same name as their nick, and get_source_mask() is
  nick!user@vhost. Somewhat longer results apply in
  other cases.
  

  Changes:	Modified:
  +3 -0		trunk/include/services.h (File Modified) 
  +61 -0	trunk/src/services.c (File Modified) 


