jilles      2006/09/14 00:58:10 UTC	(20060914-6387)
  Log:
  - Add tracking which listener (if any) a connection was accepted on
    (just a listener pointer in each connection, not a list of
    connections with each listener).
  - Add connection_close_soon(), calls the close_handler, marks the
    connection CF_DEAD and clears all handlers.
  - Add connection_close_soon_children(), calls connection_close_soon()
    for the connection itself and all connections accepted on it.
  - Use this in gen_httpd.c to avoid crashes on unload.
  

  Changes:	Modified:
  +1 -1		trunk/contrib/gen_httpd.c (File Modified) 
  +70 -0	trunk/libatheme/connection.c (File Modified) 
  +3 -0		trunk/libatheme/connection.h (File Modified) 


