jilles      2006/09/13 15:56:58 UTC	(20060913-6373)
  Log:
  - Get rid of connection_dead hook and replace it with
    close_handler callback. This way other connections
    than the ircd uplink can have special shutdown code.
  - Use the CF_DEAD flag to mark connections that got
    an error in sendq_flush() to close them when it is
    safe to do so. We may call sendq_flush() on a
    different connection than the current node in
    poll.c's LIST_FOREACH_SAFE.
  

  Changes:	Modified:
  +0 -1		trunk/doc/HOOKS (File Modified) 
  +0 -1		trunk/include/uplink.h (File Modified) 
