jilles      2006/09/08 23:14:03 UTC	(20060908-6331)
  Log:
  Add gen_vhostonreg module from atheme-modules.
  Sets a vhost on new registrations (nickserv or userserv),
  <accountname>.<hidehostsuffix> where hidehostsuffix is
  the hidehostsuffix value in serverinfo{}.
  Note that this is different from the gen_vhostonreg
  in atheme-modules which uses a custom setting.
  

  Changes:	Modified:
  +1 -0		trunk/contrib/Makefile.in (File Modified) 
  +51 -0	trunk/contrib/gen_vhostonreg.c (File Added) 


jilles      2006/09/08 22:52:31 UTC	(20060908-6329)
  Log:
  node_add(): when adding the first node to a list, make
  both head and tail point at it.
  The same configuration already exists when removing a
  node from a list with two nodes.
  

