jilles      2006/09/06 22:55:36 UTC	(20060906-6321)
  Log:
  operserv clearchan: Change syntax
  old: CLEARCHAN <#channel> [!KICK|!KILL|!GLINE] <reason>
  new: CLEARCHAN KICK|KILL|GLINE <#channel> <reason>
  This avoids ugly optional arguments in the middle.
  As before there is an undocumented alias KLINE for GLINE.
  

  Changes:	Modified:
  +3 -3		trunk/help/oservice/clearchan (File Modified) 
  +13 -35	trunk/modules/operserv/clearchan.c (File Modified) 


