  +1 -1		trunk/contrib/ns_enforce.c (File Modified) 


jilles      2006/08/31 15:23:16 UTC	(20060831-6257)
  Log:
  Add void holdnick_sts(user_t *source, int duration, const char *nick,
  myuser_t *account) protocol function, makes the given nick
  temporarily unavailable (except possibly to the given account)
  for duration seconds. A duration of 0 tries to remove the effect
  of a previous call.
  Use this in the nickserv enforce module instead of direct sts().
  Enforcers that cannot be removed are limited to 5 minutes.
  

  Changes:	Modified:
  +5 -14	trunk/contrib/ns_enforce.c (File Modified) 
