jilles      2006/08/20 14:08:59 UTC	(20060820-6167)
  Log:
  Add operserv rwatch, a list of regular expressions all
  connecting clients are matched against. Matching clients
  are described in the snoop channel and/or klined.
  All subcommands require user:auspex privilege, enabling or
  disabling klines additionally requires operserv:massakill.
  All changes are snooped, changes to kline are also sent over
  wallops. There is also full logging.
  Loading this module (as well as clones) with /os modload
  may cause strange errors about loading other modules,
  I will fix this later.
  

  Changes:	Modified:
  +1 -0		trunk/modules/operserv/Makefile.in (File Modified) 
  +465 -0	trunk/modules/operserv/rwatch.c (File Added) 


jilles      2006/08/20 13:35:26 UTC	(20060820-6165)
