jilles      2006/08/19 13:07:07 UTC	(20060819-6139)
  Log:
  Change parameter type for the channel_join and channel_part
  hooks to hook_channel_joinpart_t *.
  This structure contains just a chanuser_t pointer.
  If the user is kicked out, this pointer must be reset to
  NULL, so that further hook functions do not reference
  freed memory. As before, it is required to join a service
  before kicking out the last user. More explanation in
  channels.h.
  

  Changes:	Modified:
  +2 -2		trunk/doc/HOOKS (File Modified) 
  +12 -0	trunk/include/channels.h (File Modified) 
  +4 -5		trunk/modules/chanserv/close.c (File Modified) 
  +16 -7	trunk/modules/chanserv/main.c (File Modified) 
  +8 -3		trunk/src/node.c (File Modified) 


