jilles      2006/08/01 20:41:37 UTC	(20060801-5997)
  Log:
  Remove dictionary_set_compare_func() and instead take the
  comparison function from an extra argument to
  dictionary_create(). This prevents run-time changes to
  the comparison function possibly causing duplicates
  and crashes, and forces the user to think about the
  comparison function when creating a dictionary tree.
  CTCPs are now properly case sensitive.
  

  Changes:	Modified:
  +3 -8		trunk/include/dictionary.h (File Modified) 
