jilles      2006/07/18 11:01:09 UTC	(20060718-5903)
  Log:
  TopicLock: if the unauthorized user does not have +o/O
  (+o/O/h/H) either and cmode +t is not locked off, deop
  (deop and dehalfop) them and set +t, so as to prevent
  further topic changes.
  

  Changes:	Modified:
  +19 -5	trunk/modules/chanserv/main.c (File Modified) 


jilles      2006/07/18 10:35:50 UTC	(20060718-5901)
  Log:
  Add TOPICLOCK flag, causes ChanServ to revert topic
  changes by users without +t flag and servers.
  TOPICLOCK requires KEEPTOPIC (otherwise topic would
  be lost after every services restart, etc); enabling
  TOPICLOCK enables KEEPTOPIC also, disabling KEEPTOPIC
  disables TOPICLOCK also.
  

  Changes:	Modified:
  +15 -0	trunk/help/cservice/set_topiclock (File Added) 
  +1 -0		trunk/include/account.h (File Modified) 
  +8 -0		trunk/modules/chanserv/info.c (File Modified) 
  +30 -1	trunk/modules/chanserv/main.c (File Modified) 
