jilles      2005/12/07 23:40:46 UTC	(20051207-4025)
  Log:
  Don't allow setting +b if the user has +b, require +r.
  This prevents +f-r users from adding akicks via
  /cs flags by deliberately matching a +b hostmask entry.
  

